window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Drowning in the murky waters of the mafia, I’m determined to find a way out.</b></p> <p>I have my sights set on becoming a film producer and won’t let anything or anyone stand in my way. Then my mother marries a retired Godfather, and I get the head of the Greek mafia as a stepbrother.</p> <p>Nikolas Stathoulis is set on ruining my well-laid plans. His ruthless reputation has me running for the safety of my apartment.</p> <p>But he’s always there. On campus. In my apartment. Expecting me to play by his rules. If only I can ignore his godlike features and stop my heart from doing cartwheels at the sight of him.</p> <p>Greek God? <i>Pretty much.</i></p> <p>But he’s rude, demanding, and hell-bent on making my life a misery.</p> <p>Two can play this game…right?</p> <p>From <i>USA Today </i>and <i>Wall Street Journal </i>bestselling author Michelle Heard comes a standalone Greek mafia romance.</p> <p>This book is intended for mature listeners.</p>"; 
